query:
UPDATE workflow_runs
            SET status = $1,
                updated_at = $2
            WHERE id = $3
            RETURNING
                id as "id!: String",
                job_id as "job_id!: String",
                status as "status!: String",
                created_at as "created_at!: chrono::DateTime<chrono::Utc>",
                updated_at as "updated_at!: chrono::DateTime<chrono::Utc>"
